  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\n[Bitwise LMD-GHOST](https://ethresear.ch/t/bitwise-lmd-ghost/4749) is a fork choice algorithm which selects the chain which has the most votes. The algorithm is here: [bitwise_lmd_ghost](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/eth2/fork_choice/src/bitwise_lmd_ghost.rs). The testing framework is [here](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/eth2/fork_choice/tests/tests.rs). \r\n\r\nThe tests import abstract YAML tests, the format is discussed in this [thread](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-test-generators/issues/12). \r\n\r\nIt would be nice to have extended tests in [this](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/eth2/fork_choice/tests/bitwise_lmd_ghost_test_vectors.yaml) YAML file to verify the correct implementation of the algorithm. \r\n\r\nThis issue requires adding test cases to the YAML file and running `cargo test` inside the `fork-choice` crate to verify the new tests. Any tests that do not pass as expected, can be raised with @AgeManning. \r\n",
